and the door was always open and in the best

00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:47.970
possible manner. Nothing was difficult here.
Most of the modules was studied online and

00:02:47.970 --> 00:02:55.950
the evenings, weekends, we commended exams,
but if we were stuck we would phone in and

00:02:55.950 --> 00:03:01.120
